<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No...</font>

6
00:00:11,750 --> 00:00:13,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, get to Gion.</font>

7
00:00:13,320 --> 00:00:15,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hear he slit his belly in a party room.</font>

8
00:00:15,200 --> 00:00:16,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What an awful mess.</font>

9
00:00:16,510 --> 00:00:17,540
