32
00:01:58,730 --> 00:02:00,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nio, don't look.</font>

33
00:02:01,520 --> 00:02:03,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I'll be fine.</font>

34
00:02:04,010 --> 00:02:05,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't force yourself.</font>

35
00:02:05,350 --> 00:02:09,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll look. I need to see what happened.</font>

36
00:02:14,760 --> 00:02:17,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yuck. It's a sea of blood in here.</font>

37
00:02:17,280 --> 00:02:18,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He sure wasn't subtle about it.</font>

38
00:02:23,780 --> 00:02:27,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pay the proprietor.
Cleaning fees included.</font>

39
00:02:27,040 --> 00:02:29,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Call some people to remove the body.</font>

40
00:02:29,210 --> 00:02:30,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No need, sir.</font>

41
00:02:30,270 --> 00:02:33,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have already received full payment.</font>

42
00:02:33,440 --> 00:02:34,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

43
00:02:34,830 --> 00:02:36,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A bit before they found the body,</font>

44
00:02:37,020 --> 00:02:42,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">a big man in a white coat
sauntered out covered in blood spatter.</font>

45
00:02:42,450 --> 00:02:44,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Serizawa. Who else could it be?</font>

46
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:50,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why would Commander Niimi kill himself?</font>

47
00:02:50,730 --> 00:02:51,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Beats me.</font>

48
00:02:51,800 --> 00:02:55,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe he was raising funds in secret 
and had to take responsibility?</font>

49
00:02:56,040 --> 00:02:59,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You dopes. Serizawa got him, obviously.</font>

50
00:02:59,050 --> 00:03:02,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, you mean Serizawa killed him 
and made it look like seppuku?</font>

51
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:05,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><b><font size="22"><font color="#18181b">Stay
out</font></font></b></font></font>

52
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:05,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><b><font size="22"><font color="#18181b">No 
\h\hpeek-
\h\hing</font></font></b></font></font>

53
00:03:02,750 --> 00:03:04,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't see how that's possible.</font>

54
00:03:05,480 --> 00:03:08,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Niimi must have slit his own stomach.</font>

55
00:03:08,760 --> 00:03:10,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He had no other unusual wounds.</font>

56
00:03:11,250 --> 00:03:15,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Asano-sensei here is an ex-doctor.
We should trust him on this.</font>

57
00:03:15,780 --> 00:03:18,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure someone else 
beheaded him, of course.</font>

58
00:03:19,490 --> 00:03:21,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That'll be Serizawa.</font>

59
00:03:21,350 --> 00:03:23,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He threatened Niimi-san into seppuku.</font>

60
00:03:23,910 --> 00:03:25,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's hard to believe.</font>

61
00:03:26,080 --> 00:03:30,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whatever Commander Niimi intended, 
we have to face facts.</font>

62
00:03:31,020 --> 00:03:31,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The problem is...</font>

63
00:03:32,870 --> 00:03:36,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we inspectors have lost 
a leader we can't replace.</font>

64
00:03:37,740 --> 00:03:40,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So what are we going to do now?</font>

65
00:03:41,450 --> 00:03:42,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why?</font>

66
00:03:43,340 --> 00:03:46,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll take it from here. This is my job.</font>

67
00:03:47,780 --> 00:03:50,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The measure of a samurai is his death.</font>

68
00:03:51,010 --> 00:03:52,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There's more to this.</i></font>

69
00:03:53,490 --> 00:03:54,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong?</font>

70
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:56,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, nothing.</font>

71
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:59,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Think. What's going to happen next?</i></font>

72
00:04:00,470 --> 00:04:01,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What...</i></font>

73
00:04:02,130 --> 00:04:06,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#ffffff">I can't defend more than 
this mat I'm sitting on.</font></font>

74
00:04:06,640 --> 00:04:08,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What can I do?</i></font>

75
00:04:14,760 --> 00:04:16,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't tell me...</font>

76
00:04:16,010 --> 00:04:19,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yamanami, what will happen 
is a foregone conclusion.</font>

77
00:04:19,850 --> 00:04:22,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Interpret it however you 
need to after the fact.</font>

78
00:04:22,920 --> 00:04:27,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#ffffff">What a surprise. 
I hold an entirely different view.</font></font>

79
00:04:27,410 --> 00:04:30,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Niimi-san, you were an admirable man.</i></font>

80
00:04:32,130 --> 00:04:35,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can't afford to let discord 
in our ranks get any worse.</font>

81
00:04:38,050 --> 00:04:40,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't it time we did something?</font>

82
00:04:40,170 --> 00:04:41,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know.</font>

83
00:04:42,840 --> 00:04:43,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Toshi.</font>

84
00:04:44,520 --> 00:04:45,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We need to talk.</font>

85
00:04:46,010 --> 00:04:47,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Somewhere we won't be overheard.</font>

86
00:04:59,440 --> 00:05:01,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Serizawa-san must die.</font>

87
00:05:01,770 --> 00:05:02,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will kill him.</font>

88
00:05:03,980 --> 00:05:06,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-Why, though? You said to wait before.</font>

89
00:05:07,420 --> 00:05:09,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The month I stipulated has passed.</font>

90
00:05:10,220 --> 00:05:14,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I may ask, what was 
that month's reprieve for?</font>

91
00:05:16,070 --> 00:05:17,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I cannot say.</font>

92
00:05:26,770 --> 00:05:27,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

93
00:05:28,890 --> 00:05:30,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't let you join in.</font>

94
00:05:31,070 --> 00:05:34,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need you to stay out of this plan.</font>

95
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:40,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you want to ruin everything?</font>

96
00:05:41,390 --> 00:05:42,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What will I ruin?</font>

97
00:05:42,970 --> 00:05:46,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By losing, you mean? 
Would that inconvenience you?</font>

98
00:05:46,840 --> 00:05:48,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not what I mean.</font>

99
00:05:48,360 --> 00:05:51,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If word gets out you killed him
 over a grudge,</font>

100
00:05:51,680 --> 00:05:54,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">what happens to we Miburo 
under the banner of "sincerity"?</font>

101
00:05:55,200 --> 00:05:59,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'll be all over. No, you can't
 be there when it happens.</font>

102
00:05:59,710 --> 00:06:01,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is no grudge.</font>

103
00:06:01,540 --> 00:06:04,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dueling man-against-man 
is the samurai way.</font>

104
00:06:04,890 --> 00:06:07,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is about manhood and humanity.</font>

105
00:06:08,840 --> 00:06:09,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fine.</font>

106
00:06:11,080 --> 00:06:12,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kill me, then.</font>

107
00:06:13,190 --> 00:06:16,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Otherwise, I'm leaving the Miburo 
and going back to Edo.</font>

108
00:06:18,480 --> 00:06:20,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Make your choice.</font>

109
00:06:20,440 --> 00:06:23,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will you let me do this my way?</font>

110
00:06:23,240 --> 00:06:26,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or will you do it your way 
in a Miburo without me?</font>

111
00:06:37,650 --> 00:06:38,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Very well.</font>

112
00:06:40,680 --> 00:06:44,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I realize that I forced you 
to delay in the first place.</font>

113
00:06:45,450 --> 00:06:48,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The matter is entirely in your hands.</font>

114
00:06:50,450 --> 00:06:54,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But, Toshi, you cannot 
defeat Serizawa-san.</font>

115
00:06:55,360 --> 00:06:56,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know that.</font>

116
00:06:57,640 --> 00:06:58,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll do it.</font>

117
00:06:59,890 --> 00:07:01,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll kill Serizawa-san.</font>

118
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:06,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. Very well.</font>

119
00:07:08,960 --> 00:07:10,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hold your horses.</font>

120
00:07:10,480 --> 00:07:11,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Harada-san?</font>

121
00:07:11,710 --> 00:07:14,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm gonna kill that bastard Serizawa.</font>

122
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:16,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You couldn't do it.</font>

123
00:07:17,430 --> 00:07:19,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I said <i>I'm</i> gonna do it!</font>

124
00:07:19,920 --> 00:07:22,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hasumukai! Hasumukai!</font>

125
00:07:22,340 --> 00:07:25,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you, Harada-san.</font>

126
00:07:27,960 --> 00:07:29,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going to do it.</font>

127
00:07:30,840 --> 00:07:33,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on. We can't fall out <i>now</i>.</font>

128
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:36,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We should settle this the Shieikan way.</font>

129
00:07:36,720 --> 00:07:38,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A duel it is, then.</font>

130
00:07:38,470 --> 00:07:39,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't see why not.</font>

131
00:07:39,790 --> 00:07:41,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bring it on.</font>

132
00:07:48,800 --> 00:07:49,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nagakura?</font>

133
00:07:51,410 --> 00:07:53,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I cannot bring myself to do this.</font>

134
00:07:55,640 --> 00:07:58,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't blame him, 
not when he's training Taro.</font>

135
00:07:58,470 --> 00:08:03,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He practices the same style as Serizawa. 
That may give him pause.</font>

136
00:08:03,910 --> 00:08:07,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He just wants to stick to his principles.</font>

137
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:08,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's the kind of man he is.</font>

138
00:08:09,450 --> 00:08:11,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you've got a shot but I don't?</font>

139
00:08:11,990 --> 00:08:13,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's put that to the test.</font>

140
00:08:13,910 --> 00:08:15,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, we shall.</font>

141
00:08:17,750 --> 00:08:19,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Spears are tricky.</font>

142
00:08:20,330 --> 00:08:22,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They have an overwhelming 
advantage in reach.</font>

143
00:08:23,210 --> 00:08:26,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And Sanosuke's spear 
reaches farther than most.</font>

144
00:08:26,680 --> 00:08:29,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you'd only know that
if you'd already fought him.</font>

145
00:08:30,690 --> 00:08:33,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He usually sticks to a sword 
when he spars with us.</font>

146
00:08:33,570 --> 00:08:37,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No doubt he feels the advantage 
a spear gives him is unfair.</font>

147
00:08:37,520 --> 00:08:41,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, when fighting a spearman, 
it's all about how to get in close.</font>

148
00:08:42,330 --> 00:08:45,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even Soji will have a hard time.</font>

149
00:08:48,380 --> 00:08:49,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's backwards.</font>

150
00:08:49,470 --> 00:08:50,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

151
00:08:50,720 --> 00:08:52,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okita's using a reverse grip.</font>

152
00:09:01,400 --> 00:09:05,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You see, I'll do whatever it takes 
to accomplish my goal.</font>

153
00:09:08,940 --> 00:09:11,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A far cry from a samurai, I know.</font>

154
00:09:12,340 --> 00:09:14,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I'd say I win.</font>

155
00:09:16,150 --> 00:09:17,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that even allowed?</font>

156
00:09:18,570 --> 00:09:21,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You sure you wanna treat your sword 
that way? It'll break on you.</font>

157
00:09:21,910 --> 00:09:24,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was already chipped.</font>

158
00:09:24,430 --> 00:09:27,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was going to get a new one 
from Sakura-san tomorrow.</font>

159
00:09:30,040 --> 00:09:32,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hijikata! When do we do it, and where?</font>

160
00:09:32,240 --> 00:09:33,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have you worked out a plan yet?</font>

161
00:09:33,960 --> 00:09:34,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tell us!</font>

162
00:09:41,630 --> 00:09:42,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fine.</font>

163
00:09:43,320 --> 00:09:46,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We move in five days, 
on the 18th of the ninth month.</font>

164
00:09:47,020 --> 00:09:48,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why that day?</font>

165
00:09:49,420 --> 00:09:52,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our whole force is supposed 
to be partying in Shimabara.</font>

166
00:09:53,240 --> 00:09:58,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The reward for our work during the coup
and mopping up will pay for it.</font>

167
00:09:58,360 --> 00:10:00,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's been planned for a while.</font>

168
00:10:00,680 --> 00:10:03,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Serizawa and company 
will be there, of course.</font>

169
00:10:03,320 --> 00:10:06,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So we get them dead drunk, 
then just plain dead?</font>

170
00:10:06,320 --> 00:10:09,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But what if they don't 
drink that heavily?</font>

171
00:10:09,820 --> 00:10:11,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We give them sleeping powder.</font>

172
00:10:12,330 --> 00:10:13,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That won't be a problem.</font>

173
00:10:14,570 --> 00:10:17,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll call three litters 
to take them home.</font>

174
00:10:17,120 --> 00:10:19,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everything before that is set up.</font>

175
00:10:19,380 --> 00:10:23,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But the Yagis have small children 
and relatives in the house.</font>

176
00:10:23,640 --> 00:10:28,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And Serizawa-san and his friends 
sometimes invite geisha or mistresses.</font>

177
00:10:30,090 --> 00:10:33,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you really ensure 
there will be no witnesses?</font>

178
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:37,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Hishiya's proprietress, Oume,
 Itosato of the Wachigaiya,</font>

179
00:10:37,960 --> 00:10:39,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and Kichiei of the Kikyoya?</font>

180
00:10:41,290 --> 00:10:42,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They won't be a problem, either.</font>

181
00:10:42,950 --> 00:10:47,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We won't let them reach the Yagi house. 
I'll bribe the litter bearers.</font>

182
00:10:48,440 --> 00:10:51,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll strike in the middle of the paddies
 between Shimabara and Mibu.</font>

183
00:10:52,300 --> 00:10:54,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll have the bearers clear out first.</font>

184
00:10:55,480 --> 00:10:57,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can tell them we want
 to watch the fireflies.</font>

185
00:10:58,370 --> 00:11:02,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then we quietly skewer them,
 litters and all.</font>

186
00:11:02,890 --> 00:11:06,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If that doesn't kill them, a bad wound
 will make them easy pickings.</font>

187
00:11:07,690 --> 00:11:11,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then we blame Choshu extremists
 and call it a night.</font>

188
00:11:11,720 --> 00:11:14,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So that's why you said 
I couldn't pull it off.</font>

189
00:11:14,640 --> 00:11:19,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you hesitate to
 kill a drunk in a litter?</font>

190
00:11:19,700 --> 00:11:21,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know I wouldn't.</font>

191
00:11:23,210 --> 00:11:25,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good thing Shinpachi's not here.</font>

192
00:11:26,200 --> 00:11:30,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kondo-san and Nagakura-san 
wouldn't take kindly to our plan.</font>

193
00:11:30,250 --> 00:11:33,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We need to do this 
without anyone getting hurt.</font>

194
00:11:33,830 --> 00:11:37,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take no chances. 
No one can ever know it was us.</font>

195
00:11:37,980 --> 00:11:40,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Soji and I will kill Serizawa.</font>

196
00:11:40,960 --> 00:11:44,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fine. I'll kill Hirayama.</font>

197
00:11:44,020 --> 00:11:47,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But don't forget Hirama. 
We need one more guy.</font>

198
00:11:48,210 --> 00:11:49,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I volunteer.</font>

199
00:11:50,160 --> 00:11:53,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yamanami. Do you understand
 what that means?</font>

200
00:11:54,240 --> 00:11:56,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You need someone prepared 
to do what it takes.</font>

201
00:11:57,250 --> 00:11:59,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who better than me?</font>

202
00:12:01,910 --> 00:12:02,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fine.</font>

203
00:12:03,300 --> 00:12:04,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about Noguchi-kun?</font>

204
00:12:05,160 --> 00:12:07,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We don't need to kill their errand boy.</font>

205
00:12:07,950 --> 00:12:10,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll send him to Osaka 
on "official business."</font>

206
00:12:10,860 --> 00:12:12,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gen-san, will you take him?</font>

207
00:12:13,970 --> 00:12:16,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hijikata, would you mind 
answering one question?</font>

208
00:12:16,970 --> 00:12:21,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know Serizawa crossed a line, 
and there's the secret order from Aizu,</font>

209
00:12:21,710 --> 00:12:25,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but is that really all this is about?</font>

210
00:12:25,820 --> 00:12:29,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you sure you don't have 
a more personal reason?</font>

211
00:12:40,990 --> 00:12:43,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't have to join us 
if you have doubts.</font>

212
00:12:43,500 --> 00:12:45,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We only need you to keep your mouth shut.</font>

213
00:12:45,800 --> 00:12:47,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I never said I wasn't gonna do it.</font>

214
00:12:48,170 --> 00:12:49,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're forgetting someone.</font>

215
00:12:51,340 --> 00:12:52,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Taro.</font>

216
00:12:52,720 --> 00:12:56,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He'll stick with Serizawa 
to the bitter end.</font>

217
00:12:57,290 --> 00:12:59,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hajime, he's your job.</font>

218
00:12:59,720 --> 00:13:01,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You want me to kill him?</font>

219
00:13:01,840 --> 00:13:04,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't even joke about that!
In that case, <i>you</i> handle Taro!</font>

220
00:13:04,890 --> 00:13:06,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll</i> kill Serizawa.</font>

221
00:13:07,380 --> 00:13:08,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't mean that.</font>

222
00:13:10,000 --> 00:13:10,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What, then?</font>

223
00:13:13,410 --> 00:13:15,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want you to save Taro.</font>

224
00:13:50,350 --> 00:13:53,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an9}<b><font size="18"><font face="Georgia">18th of the 9th month, Bunkyu 3 
(October 30th, 1863)</font></font></b></font>

225
00:13:54,870 --> 00:13:56,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's really coming down, huh?</font>

226
00:13:57,060 --> 00:13:59,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been feeling gloomy all day.</font>

227
00:13:59,800 --> 00:14:01,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is a good omen!</font>

228
00:14:01,680 --> 00:14:03,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A rain of blessings!</font>

229
00:14:04,110 --> 00:14:05,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Masa-san. Yashiro-san.</font>

230
00:14:05,870 --> 00:14:07,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Woo-hoo!</font>

231
00:14:07,290 --> 00:14:10,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Today, we party!</font>

232
00:14:08,720 --> 00:14:10,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Yeah!</font>

233
00:14:10,380 --> 00:14:13,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're going to Shimabara 
to celebrate, aren't you?</font>

234
00:14:13,640 --> 00:14:15,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup. With pretty girls.</font>

235
00:14:15,880 --> 00:14:17,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We might even, y'know...</font>

236
00:14:17,370 --> 00:14:19,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa there. He's too young 
to hear about that.</font>

237
00:14:19,430 --> 00:14:22,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kids aren't allowed 
in the red-light district.</font>

238
00:14:25,330 --> 00:14:26,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Numskulls.</font>

239
00:14:26,680 --> 00:14:28,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad they're having fun.</font>

240
00:14:28,320 --> 00:14:32,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, I bet Commander Niimi 
wanted to celebrate, too.</font>

241
00:14:32,540 --> 00:14:34,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, he arranged the whole thing.</font>

242
00:14:35,840 --> 00:14:37,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Niimi-san did?</font>

243
00:14:38,070 --> 00:14:40,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not that it matters now that he's dead.</font>

244
00:14:41,500 --> 00:14:42,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's strange.</i></font>

245
00:14:43,150 --> 00:14:47,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Niimi-san took his own life, 
meaning he could choose the day he died.</i></font>

246
00:14:48,040 --> 00:14:50,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So he wanted the party 
to be </i>after<i> his death?</i></font>

247
00:14:51,640 --> 00:14:52,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What for?</i></font>

248
00:14:54,010 --> 00:14:56,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone's going to the party, right?</font>

249
00:14:56,510 --> 00:14:57,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

250
00:14:57,480 --> 00:15:01,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Except Inoue-san, who took Noguchi 
and some other guys to Osaka.</font>

251
00:15:01,090 --> 00:15:03,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No idea why, but I guess 
Hijikata ordered it.</font>

252
00:15:04,780 --> 00:15:07,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do something about Serizawa.</font>

253
00:15:07,320 --> 00:15:09,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I assume you know what I mean.</font>

254
00:15:09,440 --> 00:15:11,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kill Serizawa.</font>

255
00:15:11,280 --> 00:15:13,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what they meant.</font>

256
00:15:14,120 --> 00:15:16,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is this all a setup?</i></font>

257
00:15:17,350 --> 00:15:20,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A setup to help 
Hijikata-san's group kill Serizawa?</i></font>

258
00:15:21,720 --> 00:15:22,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Planned by Niimi-san?</i></font>

259
00:15:23,930 --> 00:15:26,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is Serizawa-san really 
in the dark about it?</i></font>

260
00:15:33,540 --> 00:15:34,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nagakura-san.</font>

261
00:15:35,260 --> 00:15:37,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me, but where's Hijikata-san?</font>

262
00:15:38,160 --> 00:15:39,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No idea.</font>

263
00:15:45,500 --> 00:15:48,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But look at this rain. What do we do?</font>

264
00:15:49,210 --> 00:15:49,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey.</font>

265
00:15:50,490 --> 00:15:52,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, I've gotta eat something.</font>

266
00:15:52,270 --> 00:15:53,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel like a nap.</font>

267
00:15:54,870 --> 00:15:56,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why'd they suddenly...</font>

268
00:15:56,480 --> 00:15:57,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong?</font>

269
00:15:57,930 --> 00:15:59,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're covered in sweat.</font>

270
00:16:00,240 --> 00:16:01,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's today.</i></font>

271
00:16:02,360 --> 00:16:05,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If something's going to happen, 
it'll be today.</i></font>

272
00:16:07,840 --> 00:16:08,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey!</font>

273
00:16:11,020 --> 00:16:15,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Spilled water doesn't come back. 
I can't scoop up anywhere near all of it.</i></font>

274
00:16:16,380 --> 00:16:17,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Just one mat's worth.</i></font>

275
00:16:18,800 --> 00:16:21,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But I'll still do what I can.</i></font>

276
00:16:23,080 --> 00:16:25,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The measure of a samurai is his death.</font>

277
00:16:25,820 --> 00:16:28,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I heard Serizawa-san's position.</i></font>

278
00:16:28,800 --> 00:16:30,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I possibly can...</font>

279
00:16:30,880 --> 00:16:32,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I heard his wish, too.</i></font>

280
00:16:33,580 --> 00:16:35,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What can't I compromise on?</i></font>

281
00:16:36,040 --> 00:16:37,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Which way should I steer things?</i></font>

282
00:16:39,130 --> 00:16:42,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Steel yourself. Be strong.</i></font>

283
00:16:42,810 --> 00:16:45,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Aiming for that and working toward it...</i></font>

284
00:16:47,390 --> 00:16:48,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>is what makes me, me.</i></font>

285
00:16:53,590 --> 00:16:54,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's really coming down, huh?</font>

286
00:16:57,170 --> 00:16:58,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder if it'll stop by tonight.</font>

287
00:16:59,270 --> 00:17:00,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Beats me.</font>

288
00:17:03,620 --> 00:17:06,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do your best for Taro-kun.</font>

289
00:17:14,090 --> 00:17:15,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do they all think I am?</font>

290
00:17:16,530 --> 00:17:18,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fine.</font>

291
00:17:27,840 --> 00:17:28,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who's there?</font>

292
00:17:28,720 --> 00:17:29,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's me.</font>

293
00:17:30,880 --> 00:17:34,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh? But you always come at night.</font>

294
00:17:34,610 --> 00:17:36,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're short on umbrellas.</font>

295
00:17:36,540 --> 00:17:39,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Give me all you've got. 
I'll leave the money here.</font>

296
00:17:39,740 --> 00:17:41,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take those.</font>

297
00:17:42,760 --> 00:17:45,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I may not be able to come tonight.</font>

298
00:17:46,880 --> 00:17:49,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is something special going on?</font>

299
00:17:49,500 --> 00:17:50,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing, really.</font>

300
00:17:51,360 --> 00:17:53,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just can't make it. That's all.</font>

301
00:17:54,740 --> 00:17:55,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And?</font>

302
00:17:56,540 --> 00:17:59,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I don't want you 
trying to die tonight.</font>

303
00:18:00,950 --> 00:18:04,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then tell me a story. Any story.</font>

304
00:18:04,700 --> 00:18:06,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't die if you do.</font>

305
00:18:09,050 --> 00:18:10,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me think...</font>

306
00:18:10,780 --> 00:18:12,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a man called Serizawa.</font>

307
00:18:13,930 --> 00:18:18,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's a true samurai, I guess.</font>

308
00:18:23,160 --> 00:18:24,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Taro.</font>

309
00:18:24,510 --> 00:18:26,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Give me a massage.</font>

310
00:18:26,160 --> 00:18:27,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes, sir.</font>

311
00:18:28,660 --> 00:18:30,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What's going on?</i></font>

312
00:18:30,760 --> 00:18:34,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's chewed me out and thrown stuff at me
 on sight for the past two months.</i></font>

313
00:18:35,500 --> 00:18:38,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But he's so mellow now. Almost as ifâ€”</i></font>

314
00:18:38,010 --> 00:18:41,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You call that a massage? Harder!</font>

315
00:18:41,180 --> 00:18:42,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stomp on me for all you're worth!</font>

316
00:18:53,360 --> 00:18:57,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've got some nerve, 
stepping on the face of Serizawa Kamo!</font>

317
00:18:58,320 --> 00:18:59,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm dead meat!</i></font>

318
00:19:00,350 --> 00:19:02,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bring your sword.</font>

319
00:19:03,130 --> 00:19:05,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Sir?</font>

320
00:19:07,340 --> 00:19:12,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Remove the pin and hilt and do 
maintenance, just like I showed you.</font>

321
00:19:13,590 --> 00:19:15,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You remember what to do?</font>

322
00:19:15,980 --> 00:19:16,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here.</font>

323
00:19:17,180 --> 00:19:17,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir.</font>

324
00:19:26,520 --> 00:19:29,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That thing will never look right on you.</font>

325
00:19:29,490 --> 00:19:30,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-Sorry.</font>

326
00:19:31,150 --> 00:19:33,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm parched. Get me some tea.</font>

327
00:19:33,910 --> 00:19:34,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir.</font>

328
00:19:36,590 --> 00:19:37,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's weird.</i></font>

329
00:19:38,070 --> 00:19:40,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's definitely acting weird today.</i></font>

330
00:19:41,740 --> 00:19:41,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Georgia"><font size="18"><font color="#291f18">Manly</font></font></font></b></font>

331
00:19:41,870 --> 00:19:41,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Georgia"><font size="18"><font color="#291f18">Manly</font></font></font></b></font>

332
00:19:41,990 --> 00:19:42,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Georgia"><font size="18"><font color="#291f18">Manly</font></font></font></b></font>

333
00:19:42,120 --> 00:19:42,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Georgia"><font size="18"><font color="#291f18">Manly</font></font></font></b></font>

334
00:19:42,240 --> 00:19:42,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Georgia"><font size="18"><font color="#291f18">Manly</font></font></font></b></font>

335
00:19:42,640 --> 00:19:43,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here, sir.</font>

336
00:19:42,870 --> 00:19:42,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Georgia"><font size="18"><font color="#291f18">Manly</font></font></font></b></font>

337
00:19:42,950 --> 00:19:43,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Georgia"><font size="18"><font color="#291f18">Manly</font></font></font></b></font>

338
00:19:43,040 --> 00:19:43,120
