<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You little...</font>

341
00:19:48,280 --> 00:19:49,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so sorry!</font>

342
00:19:49,410 --> 00:19:51,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll wipe it up and bring a fresh cup.</font>

343
00:20:14,840 --> 00:20:17,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's mad as hell!</i></font>

344
00:20:18,710 --> 00:20:21,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">U-Um, isn't today...</font>

345
00:20:21,150 --> 00:20:22,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Serizawa-sensei!</font>

346
00:20:23,160 --> 00:20:24,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our litters will be here soon.</font>

347
00:20:24,620 --> 00:20:25,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right.</font>

348
00:20:25,290 --> 00:20:28,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Taro, fetch my coat.</font>

349
00:20:28,050 --> 00:20:28,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir.</font>

350
00:20:33,900 --> 00:20:35,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Guess I'll go.</font>

