00:20:45,960 --> 00:20:48,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A party at the Sumiya in Shimabara!</font>

353
00:20:48,250 --> 00:20:50,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's like we're rich big shots.</font>

354
00:20:51,680 --> 00:20:55,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! Mr. Moneybags! Mr. Moneybags!</font>

