364
00:23:38,140 --> 00:23:41,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I can't begin to tell what's right.</font>

365
00:23:42,340 --> 00:23:45,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I'm just gonna do what I can.</font>

366
00:23:46,260 --> 00:23:48,320
